Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是该回舰桥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在紧张么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  有一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
