Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…由三个方向对本基地发动的导弹攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方战力呢？
